<db:title>[static] QQuaternion QTransform::fromAxisAndAngle(float <db:emphasis>x</db:emphasis>, float <db:emphasis>y</db:emphasis>, float <db:emphasis>z</db:emphasis>, float <db:emphasis>angle</db:emphasis>)</db:title>
<db:para>Creates a <db:link xlink:href="qquaternion.xml">QQuaternion</db:link> from <db:code role="parameter">x</db:code>, <db:code role="parameter">y</db:code>, <db:code role="parameter">z</db:code>, and <db:code role="parameter">angle</db:code>. Returns the resulting <db:link xlink:href="qquaternion.xml">QQuaternion</db:link>.</db:para>
</db:section>
